          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely slice the<strong> shallot<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the<strong> garlic</strong></p><p>Chop 1/2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[1]</span> <strong>red chilli </strong>into rounds, then chop the<strong> remaining chilli</strong> finely</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
