    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> white long grain rice</strong> and 400ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[800ml] </span><strong>cold water </strong>to a pot with a lid and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to very low and cook, covered, for an initial 12 min</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1649837165815-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
